flowchart TD
    A([Start]) --> B[Open Gravity landing page]
    B --> C{RSU verified?}
    C -->|No| D[Register with RSU email + one-time ID check]
    D --> E
    C -->|Yes| E{Buy or sell?}

    E -->|Sell| F[Create listing: category, price, photo, pickup area]
    F --> G{Fields valid?}
    G -->|No| H[Show required-fields error]
    H --> F
    G -->|Yes| I[Listing posted - status Available]
    I --> J[Receive contact request]

    E -->|Buy| K[Browse listings]
    K --> L[Search and filter]
    L --> M{Item found?}
    M -->|No| N[Show empty state - refine filters]
    N --> L
    M -->|Yes| O[View listing detail]
    O --> P[Send contact request]

    J --> Q{Seller accepts?}
    P --> Q
    Q -->|No| R[Decline - buyer notified]
    R --> J
    Q -->|Yes| S[Contact details revealed to both]
    S --> T[Meet on campus and complete deal]
    T --> U[Seller marks item Sold]
    U --> V([End])

    W[Admin] --> X[Verify student accounts]
    W --> Y[Remove invalid listings / correct status]
    X -.supports.-> C
    Y -.keeps clean.-> K
